---
title: Herby-Honey Halloumi & Veggie Couscous with Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Whip up a halloumi and couscous extravaganza in four easy steps. Drizzle over some honey to coat the halloumi and toss the couscous with some carrot and courgette - it will look and taste like you’ve been cooking for hours!
